title: Uta no☆Prince-sama♪ Maji Love 2000%
title_jp: うたの☆プリンスさまっ♪ マジLOVE2000%
synopsis: Entering her Master's course, Nanami Haruka is facing an even more difficult time. And she isn't the only one. The main six members of Starish are assigned new seniors to watch over them! But the seniors aren't having the best attitudes about it.
